---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Science - Neurodiagnoses">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-16">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Science & Validation</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">The scientific foundation of the Neurodiagnoses framework.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 mb-4">Peer-Reviewed Publications</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>Menéndez-González, M. (2025). Implementing a tridimensional diagnostic framework for personalized medicine in neurodegenerative diseases. <em>Alzheimer's & Dementia</em>. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/alz.14591" target="_blank" class="text-primary hover:underline">https://doi.org/10.1002/alz.14591</a></p>
                <p>Menéndez-González, M. (2023). Toward a new nosology of neurodegenerative diseases. <em>Alzheimer's & Dementia, 19</em>(8), 3731-3737. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/alz.13041" target="_blank" class="text-primary hover:underline">https://doi.org/10.1002/alz.13041</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 mb-4">Preprints</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p>Osaghae, N., & Menendez Gonzalez, M. (2025). Integrating Machine Learning Pipelines for Multimodal Biomarker Prediction in Alzheimer’s and Parkinson’s Disease: A Component of the Neurodiagnoses Framework. <em>medRxiv</em>. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.08.13.25333561" target="_blank" class="text-primary hover:underline">https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.08.13.25333561</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>